First of all, the ArduinoISP example has to be runned on Arduino. 
Then after the connections with the Attiny: 
  -external clock 16Mhz 
  -the board as well as the Processor should be Attiny84 (board manager's library: attiny by David A. Mellis)
  -the programmer has to be Arduino as ISP



Connection Breadboard:

Arduino                    Attiny84

                            5V-------------- VCC --- capacitor 104 --- GND(attiny) --- GND
Dig 52 -------------------- Pa4
Dig 50 -------------------- Pa5
Dig 51 -------------------- Pa6
Dig 10 -------------------- Reset ----------- capacitor 10 uF ---- GND
Reset -- 10 uF -- GND       PB0 --- Quarz pin1 --- capacitor 22 -- GND
                            PB1 --- Quarz pin2 --- capacitor 22 -- GND

